  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join the Online Multiplayer  Melee</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479980/extras/45d43797ce89f5507a55176e2a62c1ff.poster.avif?t=1744631697\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479980/extras/45d43797ce89f5507a55176e2a62c1ff.webm?t=1744631697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479980/extras/45d43797ce89f5507a55176e2a62c1ff.mp4?t=1744631697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Fly your dragon against waves of enemy dragons and other players in chaotic, multiplayer, classic arcade action.</i></strong></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479980/extras/86130f3d6426575d63a8def0e3cb5e49.poster.avif?t=1744631697\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479980/extras/86130f3d6426575d63a8def0e3cb5e49.webm?t=1744631697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479980/extras/86130f3d6426575d63a8def0e3cb5e49.mp4?t=1744631697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Jump into an online game easily with automated matchmaking, or play solo.</i></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479980/extras/85946ba80ca3e756103534bc839ec291.poster.avif?t=1744631697\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479980/extras/85946ba80ca3e756103534bc839ec291.webm?t=1744631697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479980/extras/85946ba80ca3e756103534bc839ec291.mp4?t=1744631697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Knock out enemies by bashing them from above.</i></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479980/extras/0a6b285dc70909b5dd15235e90b0ea4f.poster.avif?t=1744631697\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479980/extras/0a6b285dc70909b5dd15235e90b0ea4f.webm?t=1744631697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479980/extras/0a6b285dc70909b5dd15235e90b0ea4f.mp4?t=1744631697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Battle through progressively more difficult rounds</i></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479980/extras/5538ac636c487dca9f957ee0fcc9e7ff.poster.avif?t=1744631697\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479980/extras/5538ac636c487dca9f957ee0fcc9e7ff.webm?t=1744631697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479980/extras/5538ac636c487dca9f957ee0fcc9e7ff.mp4?t=1744631697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Grab power ups to help you survive and defeat the other dragons</i></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Challenge</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Jump into an online game easily with automated matchmaking<br></li><li>Play the same game offline in solo mode<br></li><li>Battle through progressively more difficult rounds<br></li><li>Bash and fight enemy birds and other players before they bash you<br></li><li>Become a Survivor by making it through all rounds before running out of lives<br></li><li>Win the melee by being the Survivor with the highest score</li></ul>",
